The paper deals with polytopes and their properties, which falls under computational geometry (cs.CG). It also involves combinatorial aspects such as counting the number of faces, which is a topic in discrete mathematics (cs.DM) and combinatorics (cs.DS). The study of Minkowski sums is related to algebraic geometry and topology, which are covered in the sub-categories of geometric topology (cs.GT) and symplectic geometry (cs.SI).
